Title: R Wrapper for VTL Engine
Author: Attilio Mattiocco, Valentino Pinna, Banca d'Italia
Maintainer: Valentino Pinna <valentino.pinna@bancaditalia.it>, Attilio Mattiocco <attilio.mattiocco@bancaditalia.it>
Description: R wrapper for VTL Engine
    This package contains functions and a shiny UI for dealing 
    with the Validation and Transformation Language v2.0.
    More about VTL (and SDMX) 
			 can be found at: <https://sdmx.org>.
Depends: R (>= 3.3.0), rJava (>= 0.8-8), R6
Imports: RJSDMX (>= 2.3-3), igraph, networkD3, shiny, shinydashboard, shinyjs, jdx, xtable, dplyr, sortable
Suggests: testthat
SystemRequirements: Java (>= 8)
